FLAMETHROWER

Category: ^gMANIPULATION^n
Duration: ^gINSTANT^n

Flamethrower is a ranged physical attack that causes direct
damage and has the chance of setting the target on fire, causing
injuries and damage to gear over time.

It can be dodged like a conventional ranged attack from a firearm.

^WSee Also: CAST^n

Also

Usage: ^gORDER <spirit> FLAMETHROWER <target>^n

This power commands the spirit to cast the spell Flamethrower
on a target. This causes damage upon hitting the target but can
also cause them to erupt in flames, causing more damage over the
following turns.

^WSee Also: ORDER^N
